name: Melffy Naptime Gathering
effect: Beast monsters you control cannot be banished by your opponent's card effects. You can send this card to the Graveyard; immediately after this effect resolves, Xyz Summon 1 Xyz Monster using monsters you control, including a "Melffy" monster. During the End Phase, if this card is in your GY: You can shuffle 2 "Melffy" cards from your GY and/or banishment into the Deck, and if you do, Set this card. You can only use each effect of "Melffy Naptime Gathering" once per turn.
